_image-container"><div> <div class="background" style="background-image:url(https://d13pix9kaak6wt.cloudfront.net/background/users/r/a/y/rayanthony_1422324185_16.png);"></div> </div></div> </div> <div class="biobox-head"> <h1 class="name"><span class="first_name-container"><span class="first_name">ray</span></span> <span class="last_name-container"><span class="last_name">anthony</span></span></h1> <h2 class="headline-container"><span class="headline">Too busy doing, to stop and say what.</span></h2> <div class="actions-container"><ul class="actions buttonbar"> <li class="button large dark grey glyph-thumbsup glyph-center" id="compliment_button" title="Send ray a compliment"> </li> <li class="button large dark grey glyph-plus glyph-center" id="add_button" title="Add ray to a collection"> </li> <li class="button large dark grey glyph-forward glyph-center" id="share_button" title="Share ray’s page"> </li> <li class="button large dark grey" id="emailme_button" title="Send ray a message">Email Me</li> </ul></div> </div> <div class="biobox-content"> <div class="video-container"><div class="video"> </div></div> </div> <div class="biobox-content"> <div class="avatar-container"></div> <div class="bio-container"><div class="bio"><p>My name is Ray, I'm a capricorn, I like sunsets, movies, walks on the beach. Lets see, I've never had so much as a dollar of funding or bank loan or credit card/line to launch a business with. I like to have a fresh core project every 2-3 years, I sometimes fear without funding I may someday have to have a business that does less than a million in revenue in the first year,or god forbid, less than 20 pt profit margin. Egad!</p><p>hmm, oh I'm not real crazy about the IRS either, feels like a one sided relationship yeah, so we don't talk all that much.</p><p>I enjoy though reading about the Apps that make all these millions I just think its really just super neat and those clever [fruit name].io domains, how adorable.</p><p>I thoroughly enjoy the Rolling Stones Keith is true.</p><p>I dislike Rhianna. We were never an item, whoever spreads that is just looking for a rise from people.</p><p>I'm more inclined to listen to a genuine but flawed vocal with meaning, than say a series of overdubs and samples layered to conform to a pattern statistically pleasing 83% of secretly polled listeners of a target demographic I've never been in.</p><p>If I didn't mention it before I am a big Stones fan and am wondering most what is Charlie Watts up to at this moment? I'm starting to obsess on it what is he thinking, and does he get uncomfortable wondering just how many people are wondering what hes thinking? nah....</p><p>Cheers!</p><p>note:</p><p>I erased the tail of that backstory, it was appropriately self affirming if you knew the story, but harsh sounding</p><p>Oh and I just checked again, and yes ISIS still totally sucks.</p></div></div> <div class="bio-import-container"></div> </div> <div class="biobox-content"> <div class="meta-container"><div class="meta"> <div class="phone-container"><ul class="phone list invisible glyph-phone"> <li>3104022782</li> </ul></div> <div class="locations-container"><ul class="list locations glyph-location"><li> <a href="https://about.me/search/place:Los%20Angeles, California Usa" itemprop="homeLocation">Los Angeles, California Usa</a> </li><li> <a href="https://about.me/search/place:San%20Francisco, California, United States" itemprop="homeLocation">San Francisco, California, United States</a> </li><li> <a href="https://about.me/search/place:san%20diego" itemprop="homeLocation">san diego</a> </li></ul></div> <div class="contact-container"><div class="contactinfo"> <ul class="list phone glyph-phone"> <li class="">3104022782</li> </ul> <ul class="list address glyph-address"> <li> <ul> <li class="address"></li> <li class="group"> <span class="city"></span> <span class="state">California</span> <span class="zip"></span></li> <li class="country">United States</li> </ul> </li> </ul> </div></div